# This repo is bash scripts + shell-sourced config. They MUST have LF endings,
# even on Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true would otherwise produce CRLF and
# break them — a CRLF blank line in .env, or a \r in a script, fails at runtime).
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
.env.example text eol=lf
